other_tests.findings: A calcified fibroid measuring 2.2 x 2.4 x 1.9 cm is seen on the right. The endometrium is homogeneous and measures 3 mm. A right paraovarian simple cyst measuring 0.8 x 0.5 x 0.6 cm is seen. The left ovary contains an echogenic focus measuring 0.4 cm, unchanged from prior study and consistent with a dermoid. There is no free fluid in the pelvis. A blind-ending structure with gut signature was identified in the right lower quadrant, measuring 7 mm proximally and 9 mm distally, noncompressible, and accompanied by increased echogenicity of the surrounding peritoneal fat.
